      %{"body" => "Lookin' pretty awesome!\r\n\r\nThree (maybe two) things:\r\n\r\n- Dedupe the rtc env stuff in production.js.\r\n- Faye is in the script tags twice, but don't we included it in the webpack bundle?\r\n- Maybe use promises to clean up the flash fallback logic.",
        "created_at" => "2016-02-19T18:54:10Z",
        "html_url" => "https://github.com/thinkthroughmath/live_teaching/pull/309#issuecomment-186359958",
        "id" => 186359958,
        "issue_url" => "https://api.github.com/repos/thinkthroughmath/live_teaching/issues/309",
        "updated_at" => "2016-02-19T18:55:13Z",
        "url" => "https://api.github.com/repos/thinkthroughmath/live_teaching/issues/comments/186359958",
        "user" => %{"avatar_url" => "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/553936?v=3",
